## Key Source Files

| File | What it does |
|---|---|
| `src/local_llm_bot/app/api.py` | FastAPI — all endpoints |
| `src/local_llm_bot/app/rag_core.py` | RAG pipeline — retrieve, rerank, generate, citations |
| `src/local_llm_bot/app/config.py` | Env var loading, RagConfig |
| `src/local_llm_bot/app/ingest/` | load → chunk → embed → upsert |
| `front_end/rag_studio.html` | Entire frontend, single file |
| `prompts/system.txt` | LLM system prompt |
| `scripts/deploy_files.sh` | ais_deploy — file routing from ~/Downloads |
| `scripts/start.sh` | ais_start — starts all services |

